Shit!

59
00:06:05,264 --> 00:06:07,129
Where are they?

60
00:06:11,904 --> 00:06:14,099
This sucks.
I liked it here.

61
00:06:52,578 --> 00:06:54,978
Hello? Mom?

62
00:06:55,047 --> 00:07:00,246
Sweet Jesus,
